&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;
	&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;报告人简介：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;胡云行，教授，美国密歇根理工大学，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;麦克阿瑟首席教授（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Charles and Carroll &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;McArthur Endowed Chair Professor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;1990&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;年获厦门大学化学博士学位；早&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;期曾在纽约州立大学水牛城分校和埃克森美孚公司（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Exxon Mobil&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;）分别担任研究员和高级工程师；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;2007&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;年开始担任密歇根理工大学终身教授。主要研究方向为&lt;span style=&quot;color:black;&quot;&gt;纳米材料、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;color:black;&apos;&gt;3D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;&quot;&gt;石墨烯、清洁能源、储氢材料、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;color:black;&apos;&gt;CO&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;&quot;&gt;转化、量子化学计算和太阳能源利用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;等。已在&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Acc. Chem. Res.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;IF=24.348&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;）、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Adv. Mater.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;IF=15.409&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;）等国际著名学术期刊发表论文&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;120&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;余篇，总引用次数超过&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;4000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;次；应邀在国际学术会议、世界著名大学和研究中心做学术报告&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;100&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;余次，先后主持国际学术会议&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;次。目前担任美国化学会能源与燃料分会和国际氢气能源协会储氢分会主席，英国皇家化学学会（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Royal Society of Chemistry&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;）和美国科学发展协会（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;American Association for the Advancement of Science&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;）会员；担任美国化学协会系列丛书主编、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;J. Mater. Chem. A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;期刊、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Nature group &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;下的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;Scientific Reports&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;等&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;个国际学术杂志编委和&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;&quot;&gt;个国际学术杂志客座主编。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;;&apos;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; 
